name: Jigsaw Manor.
description:
Note: This NFT is for PC/BROWSERS only. Use mouse to play. Do its size, load can take a few seconds. Thank you.

Jigsaw manor is my 4th NFT puzzle jigsaw. On my return to this series, I present a forshadow to my next NFT, Chapter 3: The Manor. This is the final part of a 3 part point and click game. By solving the puzzle, you unlock a small video, whose art is inspired by 1st person games from the 90s. 

I hope you like it! Enjoy and take a look at the NFT point and click game that is now available! 

Have fun!
